-- BEML Plans to Invest 2.6 Billion Rupees in First Phase of Defence Project
-- Jay Shankar
-- 2010-06-21T06:59:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/beml-plans-to-invest-2-6-billion-rupees-in-first-phase-of-defence-project.html

          
          
             BEML Ltd. plans to invest 2.6
billion rupees in the first phase of its plan to manufacture
vehicles and equipment for the defense sector, Chairman and
Managing Director V.R.S. Natarajan said in Bangalore today.  
 The state-run company will spend 1.4 billion rupees in the
second phase, Natarajan said.  
